{"id":1572,"date":"2021-07-21T17:20:55","date_gmt":"2021-07-21T17:20:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/?page_id=1572"},"modified":"2022-11-08T12:50:13","modified_gmt":"2022-11-08T12:50:13","slug":"bite-wounds","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/bite-wounds\/","title":{"rendered":"Bite Wounds"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1572\" class=\"elementor elementor-1572\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-237806f elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"237806f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-24d83c2\" data-id=\"24d83c2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8178bf5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8178bf5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Skin & Soft Tissue: Bite Wounds<\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Human Bite Wounds<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-6fba11d elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"6fba11d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6cfbc99\" data-id=\"6cfbc99\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-38172a7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"38172a7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Microbial Infection<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>High Risk of Infection<ul><li>Superficial Wounds: 2%<\/li><li>Occlusion Bites: 10%<\/li><li>Clenched-Fist Injuries (Traumatic Puch): &gt; 25%<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Most Common Organisms:<ul><li>Skin Flora (Staphylococcus &amp; Streptococcus)<\/li><li>Oral Flora (<strong>Eikenella corrodens<\/strong>, Prevotella, Fusobacterium &amp; Porphyromonas)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Uninfected: Irrigation &amp; Wound Care<ul><li>Generally Wounds Should Be Left Open to Heal by Secondary Intention &amp; Not Be Closed Primarily<\/li><li>Indications for Antibiotic Prophylaxis:<ul><li>Wounds Closed Primarily<\/li><li><strong>Wounds to Face, Hands or Genitals<\/strong><\/li><li>Close Proximity to Bones or Joints<\/li><li>Diabetic or Immunocompromised<\/li><li>Deep Wounds<\/li><li>Association with Crush Injury<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Consider Tetanus, Hepatitis &amp; HIV Prophylaxis\u00a0<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/trauma-prophylaxis\/\">*See Immunology &amp; Infection: Traumatic Infection Prophylaxis<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Infected: Wound Care &amp; Antibiotics<ul><li>May Require IV Antibiotics if Severely Ill or Rapidly Progressing<\/li><li>Surgical Debridement May Be Required<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Antibiotic Regimen (If Indicated)<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>First-Line: Amoxicillin\/Clavulanate (Augmentin)<\/strong><\/li><li>Second-Line (Penicillin Allergy): Should Cover Eikenella &amp; Anaerobes<ul><li>Eikenella Coverage:<ul><li>Trimethoprim-Sulfamethoxazole (TMP-SMX\/Bactrim)<\/li><li>Doxycycline<\/li><li>Ciprofloxacin<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Anaerobic Coverage:<ul><li>Metronidazole (Flagyl)<\/li><li>Clindamycin<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-24c888e\" data-id=\"24c888e\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-921ab31 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"921ab31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12073 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Human-Teeth.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Human-Teeth.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Human-Teeth-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Human Teeth <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ebe662d elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ebe662d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-01a427b\" data-id=\"01a427b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Common Animal Bite Wounds<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-bd932f7 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"bd932f7\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5b7068a\" data-id=\"5b7068a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff47443 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ff47443\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Microbial Infection<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Generally Polymicrobial<\/li><li>Most Common Organisms: Streptococci (#1) &amp; Staphylococci (#2)<\/li><li>Other Organisms:<ul><li><strong>Pasteurella multocida<\/strong><\/li><li>Bartonella henselae \u2013 From Cats<\/li><li>Capnocytophaga<\/li><li>Anaerobes<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Dog Bites<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Most Common Animal Bite (90%)<\/li><li>Most Common in Children<\/li><li>Tend to Be Large &amp; Open<\/li><li>Less Likely to Become Infected<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Cat Bites<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Most Common in Adult Women<\/li><li>Deeper Penetration<\/li><li>More Likely to Become Infected<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Uninfected: Irrigation &amp; Wound Care<ul><li>Indications for Antibiotic Prophylaxis:<ul><li>Wounds Closed Primarily<\/li><li>Wounds to Face, Hands or Genitals<\/li><li>Close Proximity to Bones or Joints<\/li><li>Diabetic or Immunocompromised<\/li><li>Deep Wounds<\/li><li>Association with Crush Injury<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Consider Tetanus &amp; Rabies Prophylaxis<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/trauma-prophylaxis\/\">*See Immunology &amp; Infection: Traumatic Infection Prophylaxis<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Infected: Irrigation, Wound Care &amp; Antibiotics<ul><li>May Require IV Antibiotics if Severely Ill or Rapidly Progressing<\/li><li>Surgical Debridement May Be Required<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Antibiotic Regimen (If Indicated)<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>First-Line: Amoxicillin\/Clavulanate (Augmentin)<\/strong><\/li><li>Second-Line (Penicillin Allergy): Should Cover Pasteurella &amp; Anaerobes<ul><li>Pasteurella Coverage:<ul><li>Trimethoprim-Sulfamethoxazole (TMP-SMX\/Bactrim)<\/li><li>Doxycycline<\/li><li>Ciprofloxacin<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Anaerobic Coverage:<ul><li>Metronidazole (Flagyl)<\/li><li>Clindamycin<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-bdc6f63\" data-id=\"bdc6f63\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-70a9ae6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"70a9ae6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12063 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Dog-Teeth.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Dog-Teeth.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Dog-Teeth-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Dog Teeth <sup>2<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51ca5da elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"51ca5da\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12054 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Cat-Teeth.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Cat-Teeth.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Cat-Teeth-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Cat Teeth <sup>3<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5fb86c4 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5fb86c4\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fcbf15c\" data-id=\"fcbf15c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-825fe9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"825fe9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Spider Bite Wounds<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c9f2790 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c9f2790\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a57d5c9\" data-id=\"a57d5c9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f4f4f73 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f4f4f73\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Black Widow (Latrodectus)<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Appearance: Shiny Black a Red Structure on Body<\/li><li>Habitat:<ul><li>All Throughout the US<\/li><li>Rarely Found Indoors<\/li><li>Most Commonly Found Around Homes (Garages &amp; Sheds)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Effects:<ul><li>Indistinct Local Lesions<\/li><li>Systemic Effects are Uncommon<ul><li>Muscle Pain<\/li><li>Localized Diaphoresis Around the Bite<\/li><li>Muscle Rigidity<\/li><li>Tetany &amp; Seizures<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Brown Recluse (Loxosceles)<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Appearance: Brown without Significant Distinguishing Features<\/li><li>Habitat:<ul><li>Mostly in the Mid-West &amp; South US<\/li><li>Most Common Inside Homes<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Effects:<ul><li>Red Plaque with Central Pallor<\/li><li>May Progress to Necrosis<\/li><li>Systemic Effects are Rare<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Primary Treatment: Local Wound Care &amp; Pain Management<ul><li>Consider Tetanus Prophylaxis<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Debride Necrotic Tissue Once Fully Demarcated (Avoid Early Debridement)<\/li><li>Antivenom:<ul><li>Consider for Black Widow Spiders with Moderate-Severe Envenomation Unresponsive to Supportive Cares<\/li><li>None Exist for Brown Recluse Spiders<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9cc76b9\" data-id=\"9cc76b9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c4decc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0c4decc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12049 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Black-Widow.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Black-Widow.jpg 480w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Black-Widow-300x195.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" \/><\/p><p>Black Widow <sup>4<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e10725 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1e10725\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12050 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Brown-Recluse.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Brown-Recluse.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Brown-Recluse-300x204.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Brown Recluse <sup>5<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-941299e elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"941299e\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c5ff206\" data-id=\"c5ff206\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f850205 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f850205\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Snake Bite Wounds<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-200f29e elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"200f29e\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-baa6f00\" data-id=\"baa6f00\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3769b01 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3769b01\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Systemic Effects<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Tissue Necrosis<\/li><li>Neurotoxicity (Ptosis, Drooling, Flaccid Paralysis or Gait Disturbance)<\/li><li>Coagulopathy<\/li><li>Rhabdomyolysis<\/li><li>Shock<\/li><li>*Effects Vary by the Snake &amp; Venom<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Keep Patient Calm &amp; Still<ul><li>Immobilize\/Splint the Extremity as Well<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>May Consider Pressure Bandage Immobilization (PBI)<ul><li>Venom Spread &amp; Deterioration May Occur After PBI Removal<\/li><li>PBI Should Not Be Removed Until the Patient Has Received Antivenom or they Have Been Fully Evaluated with No Evidence of Envenomation<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Keep Extremity Below the Level of the Heart \u2013 Slow Lymphatic Venom Absorption<\/li><li>Consider Antivenom Administration if Indicated<\/li><li>Local Wound Care<\/li><li>Consider Tetanus Prophylaxis<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Antivenom<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Types:<ul><li><em>Monovalent<\/em> \u2013 Developed Against a Single Species<\/li><li><em>Polyvalent<\/em> \u2013 Developed Against Multiple Different Species Sharing a Geographical Region<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Indications:<ul><li>Rhabdomyolysis<\/li><li>Severe Systemic Illness<\/li><li>Severe or Rapidly Progressing Local Effects<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Avoid Unproven Methods<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Orally \u201cSucking Out\u201d the Venom<\/li><li>Mechanical Suction Devices<\/li><li>Incision to Bleed<\/li><li>Tourniquets<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/d